data.meta_description: 20160919154009-39.ropar - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides a list of 53 graduates from the year 2016 from Ropar district in Punjab with their registration numbers, names, fathers' names, and addresses. It includes basic information about each graduate in a table format organized by serial number. The graduates are from the polling booth located at Baba Zorawar Singh Fateh Singh Khalsa Girls College in Morinda.
